---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Mesken Çatı GES | Solut Enerji"
  description="Mesken Çatı GES (Güneş Enerji Santrali) ile faturanızı sıfırlayın. Profesyonel mühendislik kadromuzla anahtar teslim çözümler sunuyoruz."
>
<main class="pt-24">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative min-h-[716px] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
<img alt="Modern Residential Solar Panels" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Modern house roof with high efficiency solar panels installed" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBnr4WauqAkwSS_OY8bfqXgdInyR9YtsNXewpBfPEs5Gi6khxhXkDSwTvpiKATIZv6PaTa8dFXvQDA1OIsLU4ELP6QQ5oHcZKsGW2tzebpCW_1PYlDRqy_891LlxzkRUJXJ9cr1swljpMPsvAhwaw-TYOdZTQd6JKR8nulnBi9rc0fPsLfFyvA_948xk0s5n8FddIWDM0PbOmygUEUDbQiIdGAIa1SEk3VsGQ2RHH_BSdwzRgfMO3MRgpnPqQG5vq8evABqMGITD4g"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/90 to-primary/40"></div>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
<div class="lg:col-span-8">
<span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase rounded-sm mb-6 font-label">
                        MESKEN ÇATI GES
                    </span>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-headline font-extrabold text-white tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-8">
                        Evinizin Enerjisini <br/> <span class="text-secondary-container">Geleceğe Dönüştürün</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-primary-fixed leading-relaxed max-w-2xl font-body">
                        Mesken Çatı GES (Güneş Enerji Santrali) ile sadece faturanızı sıfırlamakla kalmayın, karbon ayak izinizi azaltarak sürdürülebilir bir yaşamın kapılarını aralayın. Profesyonel mühendislik kadromuzla anahtar teslim çözümler sunuyoruz.
                    </p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Stats Monolith Section -->
<section class="relative z-20 -mt-16 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-1 bg-white shadow-2xl rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
<div class="p-10 bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col items-center text-center border-r border-surface-container">
<span class="text-5xl font-headline font-extrabold text-primary mb-2 tracking-tighter">%100</span>
<span class="text-sm font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant font-semibold">Enerji Bağımsızlığı</span>
</div>
<div class="p-10 bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col items-center text-center border-r border-surface-container">
<span class="text-5xl font-headline font-extrabold text-primary mb-2 tracking-tighter">25+</span>
<span class="text-sm font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant font-semibold">Yıl Performans Garantisi</span>
</div>
<div class="p-10 bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<span class="text-5xl font-headline font-extrabold text-secondary mb-2 tracking-tighter">4-6 Yıl</span>
<span class="text-sm font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant font-semibold">Yatırım Geri Dönüşü</span>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Benefits Section - Asymmetric Layout -->
<section class="py-24 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
<div class="lg:col-span-5">
<h2 class="text-4xl font-headline font-extrabold text-primary tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6">
                        Neden Solut Enerji ile Güneş Paneli Kurmalısınız?
                    </h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                        Modern mühendislik yaklaşımlarımızla, çatınızın potansiyelini maksimum verimle kullanıyoruz. Estetik tasarımı teknik mükemmellik ile birleştiriyoruz.
                    </p>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
<div class="p-3 bg-secondary-container rounded-lg text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">savings</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">Maksimum Tasarruf</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Elektrik faturalarınızı minimize edin ve enerji fiyat artışlarından etkilenmeyin.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
<div class="p-3 bg-secondary-container rounded-lg text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">eco</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">Ekolojik Katkı</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Yıllık ortalama 5 ton karbon salınımını engelleyerek doğayı koruyun.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
<div class="p-3 bg-secondary-container rounded-lg text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">real_estate_agent</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">Emlak Değeri Artışı</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Kendi enerjisini üreten bir konut, emlak piyasasında %15 daha değerlidir.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="lg:col-span-7 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="space-y-4 pt-12">
<div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/5]">
<img alt="Solar Tech" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Closeup of high efficiency blue crystalline solar cells" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA59cGhI1DklOzIpPlL5cB_6OhG8rPyFWiiztd3gokw_MC9tn-ACVgj3yAcvrGDjarDxVdldkcZcWd7fQ8RevKqeyoEWugWvSmHJjJAXv_66Y0cFIkpEMLxV77Yxj73Iw8yZpfS7EM8CqKUOzi6ftN_F6rlpbOyZW73p4XKrjjSkWc2kR3N-ACGUnuef1GXww4D4FuqT5ra_Gz5cKzBPdaOOfsMw3IP3bWrLw9MECocFRUm5kTBTBtq0wiRlGApEumFfvZCbzX2O7w"/>
</div>
<div class="bg-primary p-8 rounded-2xl text-white">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl mb-4">verified_user</span>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Tier-1 Kalite</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-primary-fixed-dim">Dünyanın en iyi panel ve inverter üreticileri ile çalışıyoruz.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-4">
<div class="bg-secondary-container p-8 rounded-2xl text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl mb-4">monitoring</span>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Mobil İzleme</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-secondary-container">Üretiminizi her an akıllı telefonunuzdan takip edin.</p>
</div>
<div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/5]">
<img alt="Residential Solar" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Modern architecture home with integrated solar panel system" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBu_U87hbnOhip5P0Az-_ObeVvphfJ_tXeuvSu0LAS07ThMKNXB-mwtbN1xXySu4gwd5FxjG9DsWNgipSoFyHnZ76GJcXdK1NFlwB3SMiFysgMW6zTrN13tqrp71gGq2YFVxo6RA6etl-4IN2RbRgR-kH491icqGcDKvwS9vW2RjGew1W-2p5gDDm2JENw35bhkhV_NS36t09PifMbD8MNNP1WWwlwYAl_xntX4VSoA5Cbnri5gD_0DbqzfBIF24xqrN0nVlU73q7s"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Process Section - Kinetic Flow -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-low">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
<div class="mb-16">
<span class="text-secondary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase font-label">Süreç Yönetimi</span>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-headline font-extrabold text-primary mt-2">Nasıl Çalışıyoruz?</h2>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
<!-- Step 1 -->
<div class="relative group">
<div class="text-8xl font-headline font-black text-primary/5 absolute -top-8 -left-4">01</div>
<div class="relative z-10 pt-4">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Keşif ve Analiz</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                                Uzman ekibimiz çatınızı ve tüketim alışkanlıklarınızı yerinde inceler, teknik fizibilite raporu hazırlar.
                            </p>
</div>
<div class="mt-6 h-1 w-full bg-surface-container-highest group-hover:bg-secondary transition-colors"></div>
</div>
<!-- Step 2 -->
<div class="relative group">
<div class="text-8xl font-headline font-black text-primary/5 absolute -top-8 -left-4">02</div>
<div class="relative z-10 pt-4">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Projelendirme</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                                Statik hesaplamalar ve elektriksel tasarımlar yapılarak yasal izin süreçleri başlatılır.
                            </p>
</div>
<div class="mt-6 h-1 w-full bg-surface-container-highest group-hover:bg-secondary transition-colors"></div>
</div>
<!-- Step 3 -->
<div class="relative group">
<div class="text-8xl font-headline font-black text-primary/5 absolute -top-8 -left-4">03</div>
<div class="relative z-10 pt-4">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Kurulum</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                                Mühendis denetiminde, İSG kurallarına uygun olarak montaj ve devreye alma işlemleri tamamlanır.
                            </p>
</div>
<div class="mt-6 h-1 w-full bg-surface-container-highest group-hover:bg-secondary transition-colors"></div>
</div>
<!-- Step 4 -->
<div class="relative group">
<div class="text-8xl font-headline font-black text-primary/5 absolute -top-8 -left-4">04</div>
<div class="relative z-10 pt-4">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Bakım &amp; Destek</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                                Uzaktan izleme ve periyodik bakımlarla sisteminizin 25 yıl boyunca verimli çalışmasını sağlıyoruz.
                            </p>
</div>
<div class="mt-6 h-1 w-full bg-surface-container-highest group-hover:bg-secondary transition-colors"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Contact Section - Glassmorphism & Tonal Layering -->
<section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-primary-container/10 -skew-x-12 translate-x-32"></div>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
<div>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-headline font-extrabold text-primary mb-6">Güneşin Gücünü <br/>Evinize Taşıyın</h2>
<p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-10">
                            Ücretsiz saha keşfi ve maliyet analizi için formu doldurun. Mühendislerimiz 24 saat içinde sizinle iletişime geçsin.
                        </p>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">call</span>
<span class="font-bold text-primary">+90 (212) 555 0101</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">mail</span>
<span class="font-bold text-primary">solar@solutenerji.com</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl kinetic-monolith-shadow border border-outline-variant/10">
<form class="space-y-6" action="https://formspree.io/f/FORM_ID_HERE" method="POST">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-xs font-bold font-label uppercase text-on-surface-variant tracking-wider">Ad Soyad</label>
<input class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-outline-variant focus:border-primary focus:ring-0 transition-colors py-3 text-sm" placeholder="John Doe" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-xs font-bold font-label uppercase text-on-surface-variant tracking-wider">Telefon</label>
<input class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-outline-variant focus:border-primary focus:ring-0 transition-colors py-3 text-sm" placeholder="+90 5xx" type="tel"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-xs font-bold font-label uppercase text-on-surface-variant tracking-wider">Email Adresi</label>
<input class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-outline-variant focus:border-primary focus:ring-0 transition-colors py-3 text-sm" placeholder="email@adresi.com" type="email"/>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-xs font-bold font-label uppercase text-on-surface-variant tracking-wider">Çatı Tipi</label>
<select class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-outline-variant focus:border-primary focus:ring-0 transition-colors py-3 text-sm">
<option>Müstakil Ev</option>
<option>Apartman / Site</option>
<option>Villa</option>
<option>Diğer</option>
</select>
</div>
<div class="pt-4">
<button class="w-full bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container font-headline font-extrabold py-4 rounded-md hover:bg-secondary-fixed transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2" type="submit">
                                    Ücretsiz Analiz İsteyin
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
</button>
</div>
<p class="text-[10px] text-center text-on-surface-variant">
                                Gönder butonuna basarak Veri Politikamızı kabul etmiş olursunuz.
                            </p>
</form>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
